Usage: [KPKG_DIR=~/kpkg] #{bold}kpkg#{reset} PKG [OPTION â€¦] COMMAND [ARG â€¦] â€¦
ðŸ¢ #{title}Options :#{reset}
    --arch ARCH          build for $ARCH
